		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Nice project <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /> I wonder if your daughters appreciated it properly because it's for the NES and all, and that comes with high limitations by today's standards.<br /><br />The biggest hint I can give graphically right now is to be careful about the colors used on the background details as they seemed like interactive objects (some paintings and doors). I figure if you didn't use black for those it wouldn't give that feeling.<br />I really like the songs! Did you compose it?

		

		</td>
