		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />oh, i think the game has more merits than just the music!  It's a game i think anybody can pick up and enjoy, which is a great plus. Also, I like that there is kind of a &quot;dirty house&quot; theme going on with the cobweb, the possessed vacuum cleaners. That's a nice contrasting background subtheme to the main objective of getting birthday presents. It creates a nice tension that not every game has.<br /><br />Definitely agree that music and sound has a very strong impact on memory (and feelings).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
